Key Changes Made:
1. Theme Matching:
Applied the same color scheme as your store component

Used matching mat-header-style class for table headers

Applied same background colors (#fafafa, lightgray for headers)

Matched the mintcream hover effect on table rows

2. Filter Section:
Set filters to be always expanded by default (removed collapse/expand logic from template)

Added a user-controlled collapse toggle at the bottom of the filter section

Maintained the same filter styling and layout structure as your store component

3. Table Styling:
Matched table card styling with same box-shadow and border-radius

Applied same header styling with lightgray background

Used same row heights and hover effects

Applied consistent cell padding and text styling

4. Pagination:
Moved pagination to bottom in a separate footer section

Removed the top pagination completely

Added records count display alongside pagination

Used same paginator styling as store component

5. Layout Structure:
Maintained toolbar at top with navigation

Filter section with user-controllable collapse

Main content area with table

Footer with records info and pagination at bottom

The component now matches your store component's theme perfectly while maintaining the functionality you requested!
